title: The Ontario Readers Third Book
creator: Ontario Ministry of Education
description: LibriVox recording of The Ontario Readers Third Book, by The Ontario Ministry of Education. The Ontario Readers is a school book first published in 1919, by the Ontario Ministry of Education, containing short excerpts of literary works, both stories and poems, geared to grade-school age children. (Summary by aradlaw) For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
